descp2: string in ['raw_values', 'uniform_average']             or array-like of shape (n_outputs) Defines aggregating of multiple output values. Array-like value defines weights used to average errors. 'raw_values' : Returns a full set of errors when the input is of multioutput format. 'uniform_average' : Errors of all outputs are averaged with uniform weight.
